<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="no-js" lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>404 Not Found</title>
    
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cfaadigest.com/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.2/css/all.min.css">
    
    
    <style>
        .not-found {
            padding: 6rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            min-height: 60vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .not-found__title {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: var(--color-primary, #e22d30);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .not-found__text {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--color-text-secondary, #666);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .not-found__help {
            color: var(--color-text-secondary, #666);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .not-found__links {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .not-found__links .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            background: var(--color-primary, #e22d30);
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 3px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .not-found__links .button:hover {
            background: var(--color-primary-dark, #c41c1f);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container container--outer">
        <main class="main full-width" role="main">
            <div class="not-found">
                <h1 class="not-found__title"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> 404</h1>
                <p class="not-found__text">Sorry, the page you requested does not exist</p>
                <p class="not-found__help">Here are some helpful links instead:</p>
                <div class="not-found__links">
                    <a href="https://cfaadigest.com/" class="button">
                        <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Home
                    </a>
                    
                    
                        
                            <a href="https://cfaadigest.com/posts/the-inspiring-journey-of-jesse-k-sanchez-a-trailblazer-in-personal-development/" class="button">
                                <i class="fas fa-link"></i> The Inspiring Journey of Jesse K Sanchez: A Trailblazer in Personal Development
                            </a>
                        
                    
                        
                            <a href="https://cfaadigest.com/posts/framework-how-the-nist-cybersecurity-framework-shapes-legal-strategy/" class="button">
                                <i class="fas fa-link"></i> Framework: How the NIST Cybersecurity Framework Shapes Legal Strategy
                            </a>
                        
                    
                        
                            <a href="https://cfaadigest.com/posts/regulation-navigating-cybersecurity-compliance-with-expert-analysis/" class="button">
                                <i class="fas fa-link"></i> Regulation: Navigating Cybersecurity Compliance with Expert Analysis
                            </a>
                        
                    
                        
                            <a href="https://cfaadigest.com/posts/cfaa-key-legal-insights-every-cybersecurity-lawyer-must-know/" class="button">
                                <i class="fas fa-link"></i> CFAA: Key Legal Insights Every Cybersecurity Lawyer Must Know
                            </a>
                        
                    
                        
                            <a href="https://cfaadigest.com/posts/understanding-bright-bail-bonds-your-guide-to-legal-help/" class="button">
                                <i class="fas fa-link"></i> Understanding Bright Bail Bonds: Your Guide to Legal Help
                            </a>
                        
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

    
    <script async defer src="https://cfaadigest.com/js/menu.js"></script>
</body>
</html>